                        <p><h5>Openfarm operates http://www.openfarm.com.ng. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from applicants. 

                        We use your Personal Information only for verification and connecting you with farmers who need your services from our business solutions. By using applying as a farm manager, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. 

                        Information Collection And Use 

                        While filling the application form, we will like you provide personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to your name ("Personal Information").</h5></p> 

                        <h4><a href="#">Log Data</a></h4> 

                        <p><h5>Like many site operators, we collect information that your browser sends whenever you visit our Site ("Log Data"). 

                        This Log Data may include information such as your computer's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, browser type, browser version, and the pages of our Site that you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages and other statistics. 

                        In addition, we may use third party services such as Google Analytics that collect, monitor and analyze this.</h5></p>

                         <h4><a href="#">Access</a></h4> 
                        <p><h5>We may use your Personal Information to verify you and grant you access to using our business solutions such as Openfarm Manager, for managing farm production data.</h5></p>


                         <h4><a href="#">Communications</a></h4> 
                        <p><h5>We may use your Personal Information to contact you with newsletters, marketing or promotional materials and other information that will help services farmers better.</h5></p>

                        <h4><a href="#">Business</a></h4>

                        <p><h5>We send your Personal Information to farmer and they will engage you for their services. Therefore your service shall be paid by farmer and Openfarm is not and cannot be responsible of any form of payment to you.</h5></p> 

                        <h4><a href="#">Security</a></h4>

                        <p><h5>The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</h5></p> 

